Package com.pb.sawdust.util.collections.iterators

Provides a variety of iterator extensions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChainedIterator<E>
    The ChainedIterator ...
    FilteredIterator<E>
    The FilteredIterator class is used to iterate over a collection where certain values are skipped.
    IterableIterator<T>
    The IterableIterator class provides a simple wrapper to make an iterator iterable.
    ParallelIterator<E>
    The ParallelIterator class provides a framework to get identical, parallel iterators.
    ParallelRegistrationIterator<E>
    The ParallelRegistrationIterator is a ParallelIterator in which iterators are tied to specific registrants.
    TransformingIterator<F,T>
    The TransformingIterator is an iterator which wraps another iterator in a simple transformation function.
